{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_06_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 拝啓、師走の候",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "う～んいい匂いだな～\n見て見て、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ it smells so good~\nLook‚ look‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ケーキの土台は完璧な焼き上がりだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cake base has baked perfectly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1913149675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "焼き上がりはいいんだけど……\n真ん中に穴が空いてるのはどうしてだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The baking is fine‚ but…\nWhy is there a hole in the middle?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "うん！\nドーナツみたいで美味しそうでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah!\nIt's like a donut‚ doesn't it look great?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ドーナツとケーキの組み合わせで\nダブルで美味しいの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Combining donuts and cake\nmakes it doubly delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "これぞ芽衣の発明した最強スイーツだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the ultimate sweet invention by Mei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……俺はスイーツには詳しくないから\n芽衣に任せるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I'm not really knowledgeable about sweets‚\nso I'll leave it to you‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "よ～し、次は飾り付けだよ\nイチゴはたっぷり使おっと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ the next is decorating!\nLet's use plenty of strawberries!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4000,
          "startTime": 42.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 8600.000000000002,
          "startTime": 46.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-03.m4a",
          "delay": 11233.333333299996,
          "startTime": 49.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "手早く進めよう。生クリームはグラニュー糖を\n入れてよくかき混ぜるのか……案外難しいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's do quickly. Do mix sugar with whipped cream…\nIt's pretty tricky.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15066.6666667,
          "startTime": 58.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 19033.3333333,
          "startTime": 62.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんの帰りは夕方だから、じっくり丁寧に\n……って、琴乃ちゃんからメッセージだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kono-chan will be back in the evening‚ so we have to be meticulous…\n…Wait‚ I just got a message from Kono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "えっと――芽衣、今、どこにいるの？\nクリスマスライブのことで聞きたいことがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uhㅡㅡ Mei‚ where are you right now?\nI want to ask you something about the Christmas live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "……だって。ねえ、{user}さん\n琴乃ちゃん、なんか気付いてるっぽくない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…She says. Hey‚ {user}-san.\nDo you think Kono-chan has noticed something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は鋭いしな。これまでの芽衣やみんなの言動から\n何か感付いたのかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kono is sharp. Based on Mei's and everyone's actions so far‚\nshe might have noticed something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どう返事したらいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I reply?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "普段通りの芽衣でいいと思う\n変に隠そうとすると、かえって怪しまれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you should just be yourself.\nTrying to hide it might make you look suspicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かった！　いつもの芽衣だね！\nえ、えっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ got it! Just be myself‚ right?\nUmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "――拝啓。師走の候、貴方様にますますのご繁栄の\nこととお慶び申し上げます。平素は格段の厚情を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡDear Kono-chan‚ in this busy December‚ I wish your increasing prosperity.\nI humbly express my profound gratitudeㅡㅡ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "硬い、硬いって！　別人になってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Too formal‚ too formal! You're acting completely different!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ごめ～ん、もう送っちゃった\n琴乃ちゃん、凄く怪しんでるみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oops‚ I already sent it…\nIt seems like Kono-chan is really suspicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "諦めるのはまだ早いぞ\nすぐ普段の芽衣らしい返信を送って、リカバーしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's too early to give up.\nQuickly send a reply in your usual style and recover.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "普段の芽衣ってどんな感じだっけ？\n分からなくなっちゃったよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What does my usual style look like again?\nI'm not sure anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……もっと親しげで、人懐っこくて\nまっすぐな女の子だよ、芽衣は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… more friendly‚ outgoing‚ and pure-hearted.\nThat's the Mei I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうかな、照れちゃうな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehehe‚ is that so? Im a not embarrassed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今は照れてる場合じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now is not the time to be embarrassed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったね、ごめん。えっと、琴乃ちゃん、お疲れ～\n今はね、{user}さんと一緒だよ、っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ okay‚ I'll try! Um‚ let's see…\n\"Hi! It's me‚ Mei! I'm here with {user}-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺と一緒なのは、書かない方がいいんじゃないか？\nサプライズの件に気付かれるかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it okay to say I'm with you?\nShe might notice the surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、そっか。失敗失敗\n芽衣、なんでも正直に話しちゃうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right? My bad‚ my bad.\nMei is the type to blurt things out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 179.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8566.666666599986,
          "startTime": 184.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "って、琴乃ちゃんから返信だ！　早いな～\n{user}さんとどこで何してるの、だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Kotono-chan responded! That was fast~\nShe's asking where {user}-san and I are and what we're doing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "単独の仕事のことで、事務所で打ち合わせしてる\n……って伝えるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm in a meeting at the office because of my solo schedule.\n…I said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "うん、分かった。単独の仕事のことで……\n…………う～ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I understand. Because of your solo schedule…\n…Hmm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、琴乃ちゃんに嘘つきたくないな\n友達だもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei doesn't want to lie to Kotono-chan…\nWe're friends‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……芽衣らしいな。でも、寮でバースデーケーキを\n作ってるって、正直に伝える訳にもいかないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's very Mei-like‚ but even so‚ I can't honestly say\nwe're making a her birthday cake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだけど……\nなんとか嘘つかずに内緒に出来ないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…\nHow can we keep it a secret without lying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 226.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei022.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、琴乃ちゃんからまたメッセージだ\n芽衣の返信が遅いから、気にしてるみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ I got another message from Kotono-chan.\nShe's worried because Mei's replies are late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei023.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう、{user}さん、助けて～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should we do‚ {user}-san? Help me~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、寮にいることだけ伝えよう。後は何も\n心配はしなくていいって。これなら嘘じゃないだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then just say you're at the dorm‚ and there's nothing to worry about.\nThat's not a lie‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei024.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね！　……今は寮にいるよ。心配なことなんて\nなんにもないよ。安心して！　っと。ふぅ、これで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! …Right now‚ I'm at the dorm.\nThere's nothing to worry about. Feel at ease! And…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 261.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei025.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃ちゃんから返信！？　早過ぎるよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…A reply from Kotono-chan!? That was too fast!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の執念を感じるな……。なんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono's determination is something else…What should I say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei026.m4a",
      "text": "――良かった。ちょうど、私も忘れ物を取りに\n寮に向かってるから、会って話したい――だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Phew‚ that's a relief. I was just on my way to get\nsomething I forgot at the dorm. Let's talk when we see.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ここに来るのか？　マズいぞ！\n調理を中止して、ケーキと材料を隠さないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's coming here? This is bad!\nWe need to stop cooking and hide the cake and ingredients.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.7333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.999999899977,
          "startTime": 292.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei027.m4a",
      "text": "わわわ！　えっと、お皿とまな板を洗って……\n換気もしないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-w-w-what!? Then we need to wash the dishes\nand cutting board… and ventilate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei028.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、今、玄関のドアが開いた音がした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ I heard the front door opened just now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、荷物を持って庭へ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ take the stuff and go to the yard!",
