      "startTime": 308.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "間一髪だったな。俺は作りかけのケーキと材料を持って\nしばらく外にいる。芽衣は琴乃に会ってくるといい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so close. I'll carry the cake and ingredients and be outside for a while.\nMei‚ you should go see Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃は芽衣を気にしてたんだろう？\n顔を見せに行った方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was worried about you‚ right?\nSo‚ show her your face.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 323.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei030.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いろいろありがとう\n{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ thanks for everything.\n{user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei031.m4a",
      "text": "……今日のことは、芽衣と{user}さん\n二人だけの秘密だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Today's events are a secret between Mei\nand {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 332.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。でも芽衣は嘘は嫌いだって言ってたよな\n秘密は嫌じゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. But you said you don't like lying.\nWhat about secrets?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 340.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei032.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。嘘は嫌だけど、秘密ならいいかも\nなんだか特別な感じがするし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm‚ I don't like lying‚ but maybe secrets are okay.\nFor some reason‚ it feels special‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 348.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_02-mei033.m4a",
      "text": "二人だけの秘密ってさ\n仲良しじゃないと作れないもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and you can't create something like that unless\nyou get along well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 354.5,
      "sfxList": [
